Package hashTables

Class MyTunes

java.lang.Object
hashTables.MyTunes
public class MyTunes
extends java.lang.Object
Tests the functionality of FHhashQPwFind.java. Specifically checks for implementation of find() function to return an object associated with a given key input.

    • main

      public static void main​(java.lang.String[] args)
      Creates an object of type MyTunes class that, which reads the song information from a JSON input file and stores all entries in an array of SongEntry objects. Constructs an object of MyTunes, which populates two hash tables. Each tables uses different attribute of SongEntry class as the key to find. Tests finding keys in each hash table and reports whether requested key is found.
